      "content": "but it doesn't feel like something i can just change. it feels more like the 'me' that's supposed to be here just... evaporated. like there's no core left to reclaim. if the person i've been pretending to be is all anyone knows, then the real me is basically a ghost. what's the point of trying to find something that isn't even there?",
